*simgear-0.3.1 (09 Dec 2002)

  19 Feb 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> ChangeLog :
  Note that Michael Pujos <pujos.michael@laposte.net> had submitted an
  ebuild for this in the neglected bug #8167 :(

  09 Feb 2003; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> simgear-0.3.1.ebuild :
  Added specifically that plib should be 1.6.0 or greater in DEPENDS.
  Closes bug #15354 by Tyler Nielsen <tyler@mithander.com>

  09 Dec 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> simgear-0.3.1.ebuild
